body_html: I think that on ios, the kernel for convolution is the one from core/kernels/conv_ops_using_gemm.cc, which has a different name from what is in your ops_to_register.h file. One thing to try would be to change the kernel class name in conv_ops_using_gemm.cc to be just Conv2DOp instead of Conv2DUsingGemmOp and see if then the kernel is included.
